title: Flacco Trade Reaction; Antonio Brown Landing Spots
itunes:title: Flacco Trade Reaction; Antonio Brown Landing Spots
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal fill you in on all of the news around the league including Joe Flacco being traded to the Broncos (4:30), The Arizona Cardinals saying they will stick with rookie QB Josh Rosen (15:02) and Redskins players confirming they won't see QB Alex Smith in 2019 (20:01). Where will Antonio Brown end up after he publicly declared he wanted to leave the Steelers? (27:34) The heroes end the show with a segment called "big names who could be cut" (42:51).
